import { AppBar, Toolbar, Typography, Link } from '@material-ui/core'
import { useStyles } from './styles'

function Navbar() {
    const classes = useStyles();

    return (
        <AppBar
            position="static"
            color="transparent"
            elevation={0}
            className={classes.root}
        >
            <Toolbar>
                <Typography
                    variant="h5"
                    className="navbar__title"
                    component="h1"
                    className={classes.title}
                >
                    the planets
                </Typography>
                <Typography>
                    <Link 
                        href="#"
                        underline="none"
                    >
                        Link
                    </Link>
                </Typography>
            </Toolbar>
        </AppBar>
    )
}

export default Navbar
